jika Error
update user set authentication_string=password(''), plugin='mysql_native_password' where user='root';
lakukan :
1. akses bash dengan sudo su 
2. mysql -u root -p
3. use mysql 
4. update user set authentication_string=password(''), plugin='mysql_native_password' where user='root';